-:- REGISTRATION OPEN -:-<br /><br />We are now allowing registration on our forum, <br />- Forum.salafiri.com (<!-- l --><a class="postlink-local" href="https://forum.salafiri.com/index.php">index.php</a><!-- l -->)<br /><br />The number of new registrants will be limited in order to maximise benefit and to curb unnecessary discourse. We will allow people to register at later intervals through a phased process. Anyone is welcome to join.<br /><br />How to Join<br />1. Register on the forum. Use appropriate names. This is applicable to anyone who wants to contribute, discuss, share and learn.<br /><br />2. <strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #FF0000">Then send the names of two referees via the forum contact link</span></span></strong> (at the bottom of the page titled &quot;Contact us&quot;).<br /><br /><!-- l --><a class="postlink-local" href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=contactadmin">memberlist.php?mode=contactadmin</a><!-- l --><br /><br />This is to ensure i. safety, ii. accountability. <br /><br />Referees could include current registrants or members of the forum, du'at or other socially active Muslims we can contact to verify. Registrants must specify the COUNTRY and CITY they reside in. <br /><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 200%; line-height: normal">Registration WILL NOT be approved without the referees and the required information.</span></strong><br /><br />Jazakallahu Khaira<br />Salafi Research Institute.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Fri Jun 19, 2020 10:49 am</p><hr />
